  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Symptoms and signs of acute pancreatitis and if pancreatic or/and peripancreatic fluid
             collections were confirmed by ultrasound and computed tomography examination

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Collections resulting from pancreatic surgery, chronic pancreatitis and encapsulated
             collections and collections with uncertainty about the relationship between the
             collections and clinical symptoms and signs of acute pancreatitis were excluded.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
